Juventus to Meet Club America in Soccer Exhibition at Mets’ Citi Field

-- B y   L a r r y   S i d d o n s
-- 
2011-06-09T14:20:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-09/juventus-to-meet-club-america-in-soccer-exhibition-at-mets-citi-field.html
Juventus will play Club America in a
soccer match at the  New York Mets ’ Citi Field on July 26.  Juventus, a record 27-time champion of  Italy ’s top league,
and Club America, one of  Mexico ’s most popular teams, will meet
in the second soccer exhibition at the Mets’ three-year-old
stadium. Ecuador and  Greece  drew 1-1 at Citi Field two days ago.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Larry Siddons at 
 lsiddons@bloomberg.net  